message: PDF extracted and project created successfully

project.title: Brand Identity Project Brief
project.description: TechVenture is an early-stage startup disrupting the e-commerce space with AI-powered recommendations. They require a complete brand identity for an upcoming investor pitch in three weeks, seeking a modern, tech-forward, and minimal aesthetic similar to Stripe or Notion.
project.result: A comprehensive brand identity system and essential marketing assets ready for an investor pitch.

ai_researched_costs.software_needed: Adobe Creative Cloud (Illustrator, Photoshop, InDesign), Figma Professional, Google Workspace
ai_researched_costs.equipment_requirements: High-color accuracy monitor (sRGB 99%+), MacBook Pro or equivalent workstation, Graphics Tablet (optional for logos)

market_research.comparable_rates: Upwork Cambodia freelancers: $15-40/hr; Local boutique agencies in Phnom Penh: $1,500-$3,500 for full identity; Entry-level local freelancers: $400-$800.

adjustments.reason: Mid-level professional rate in Phnom Penh market ($20/hr base).
Requirement for high-end aesthetic (Stripe/Notion style) and editable templates increases technical oversight.
Early-stage startup discount applied to encourage long-term partnership.
3-week deadline for a full brand system is considered a rush project, requiring prioritized scheduling.
